          <button id="btnCancelRuleEditor" class="rounded-2xl bg-white px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 transition hover:bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 dark:text-gray-300 dark:hover:bg-gray-700" data-i18n="common.cancel">取消</button>
          <button id="btnSaveRuleEditor" class="rounded-2xl bg-primary-600 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-lg shadow-primary-600/25 transition hover:bg-primary-700" data-i18n="rule.editor.save">保存修改</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div id="stopCronModal" class="fixed inset-0 z-50 hidden">
      <div id="stopCronBackdrop" class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/50 backdrop-blur-sm opacity-0 transition-opacity"></div>
      <div id="stopCronContent" class="absolute inset-x-4 top-28 mx-auto max-w-xl translate-y-6 overflow-hidden rounded-3xl bg-gray-50 shadow-2xl transition-transform dark:bg-gray-950">
        <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4 border-b border-gray-200 px-6 py-4 dark:border-gray-800">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white" data-i18n="cron_stop.title">停止定时任务</h2>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="cron_stop.subtitle">停止后，计划任务将不会再按 Cron 自动执行。</p>
          </div>
          <button id="btnStopCronCancelTop" class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 transition hover:bg-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-800 dark:text-gray-400 dark:hover:bg-gray-700" aria-label="关闭" data-i18n-aria-label="common.close" data-i18n-title="common.close">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" />
            </svg>
          </button>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-amber-200 bg-amber-50 p-4 text-sm text-amber-800 dark:border-amber-500/30 dark:bg-amber-500/10 dark:text-amber-200">
            <div class="font-semibold" data-i18n="cron_stop.notice_title">注意</div>
            <div class="mt-2 leading-relaxed" id="stopCronHint" data-i18n="cron_stop.hint.idle">停止后可能会导致计划任务不会再执行。停止后你可以切换到 once / clean 模式执行；如需再次启动定时任务，请选择 cron 或 cronAft 模式并点击启动。</div>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-5 rounded-2xl bg-gray-100/60 p-4 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:bg-gray-900/40 dark:text-gray-300">
            <div class="font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white" data-i18n="cron_stop.status_title">当前状态</div>
            <div class="mt-2 grid gap-2 sm:grid-cols-2">
              <div><span data-i18n="cron_stop.field.module">模块</span>: <span class="font-mono" id="stopCronModule">--</span></div>
              <div><span data-i18n="cron_stop.field.cron">Cron</span>: <span class="font-mono" id="stopCronExpr">--</span></div>
              <div class="sm:col-span-2"><span data-i18n="cron_stop.field.next">下次执行</span>: <span class="font-mono" id="stopCronNext">--</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-end gap-3 border-t border-gray-200 bg-white/90 px-6 py-4 backdrop-blur dark:border-gray-800 dark:bg-gray-950/90">
          <button id="btnStopCronCancel" class="rounded-2xl bg-white px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 transition hover:bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 dark:text-gray-300 dark:hover:bg-gray-700" data-i18n="common.cancel">取消</button>
          <button id="btnStopCronConfirm" class="rounded-2xl bg-red-500 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-lg shadow-red-500/25 transition hover:bg-red-600" data-i18n="cron_stop.confirm">停止定时任务</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div id="aboutModal" class="fixed inset-0 z-50 hidden">
      <div id="aboutBackdrop" class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/50 backdrop-blur-sm opacity-0 transition-opacity"></div>
      <div id="aboutContent" class="absolute inset-x-4 top-20 bottom-8 mx-auto max-w-2xl translate-y-6 overflow-hidden rounded-3xl bg-gray-50 shadow-2xl transition-transform dark:bg-gray-950">
        <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4 border-b border-gray-200 px-6 py-4 dark:border-gray-800">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white" data-i18n="about.title">关于</h2>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="about.subtitle">项目信息与更新检查</p>
          </div>
          <button id="btnCloseAbout" class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 transition hover:bg-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-800 dark:text-gray-400 dark:hover:bg-gray-700" aria-label="关闭" data-i18n-aria-label="common.close" data-i18n-title="common.close">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" />
            </svg>
          </button>
        </div>

        <div class="h-full overflow-y-auto p-6">
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-gray-100/60 p-4 text-sm text-gray-700 dark:bg-gray-900/40 dark:text-gray-300">
              <div class="mb-2 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="about.section.info">基本信息</div>
              <div class="grid gap-2 sm:grid-cols-2">
                <div><span class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="about.info.project">项目</span>: <a class="font-mono text-primary-600 hover:underline dark:text-primary-400" href="https://github.com/joyanhui/ikuai-bypass" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">joyanhui/ikuai-bypass</a></div>
                <div><span class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="about.info.runtime">运行环境</span>: <span class="font-mono" id="aboutRuntime">--</span></div>
                <div class="sm:col-span-2"><span class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="about.info.config_path">配置路径</span>: <span class="font-mono" id="aboutConfigPath">--</span></div>
                <div class="sm:col-span-2"><span class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="about.info.http_proxy">HTTP 代理</span>: <span class="font-mono" id="aboutHttpProxy">--</span></div>
                <div class="sm:col-span-2"><span class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="about.info.github_proxy">GitHub Proxy</span>: <span class="font-mono" id="aboutGithubProxy">--</span></div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="rounded-2xl border border-primary-500/15 bg-primary-500/5 p-4 text-sm text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
              <div class="mb-3 flex items-center justify-between gap-3">
                <div>
                  <div class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="about.section.update">新版查询</div>
                  <div id="aboutUpdateHint" class="mt-1 text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400"></div>
                </div>
                <button id="btnCheckUpdate" class="rounded-xl bg-primary-600 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-primary-700" data-i18n="about.update.check">查询新版</button>
              </div>

              <div class="space-y-3">
                <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white/70 p-3 dark:bg-gray-950/40">
                  <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3">
                    <span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="about.update.stable">正式版</span>
                    <a id="aboutStableLink" class="text-xs font-medium text-primary-600 hover:underline dark:text-primary-400" href="https://github.com/joyanhui/ikuai-bypass/releases" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" data-i18n="about.update.open">打开</a>
                  </div>
                  <div class="mt-2 grid gap-1 sm:grid-cols-2">
                    <div><span class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="about.update.tag">标签</span>: <span class="font-mono" id="aboutStableTag">--</span></div>
                    <div><span class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="about.update.time">时间</span>: <span class="font-mono" id="aboutStableTime">--</span></div>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white/70 p-3 dark:bg-gray-950/40">
                  <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3">
                    <span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="about.update.prerelease">Pre-release</span>
                    <a id="aboutPreLink" class="text-xs font-medium text-primary-600 hover:underline dark:text-primary-400" href="https://github.com/joyanhui/ikuai-bypass/releases" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" data-i18n="about.update.open">打开</a>
                  </div>
                  <div class="mt-2 grid gap-1 sm:grid-cols-2">
                    <div><span class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="about.update.tag">标签</span>: <span class="font-mono" id="aboutPreTag">--</span></div>
                    <div><span class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="about.update.time">时间</span>: <span class="font-mono" id="aboutPreTime">--</span></div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-gray-100/60 p-4 text-sm text-gray-700 dark:bg-gray-900/40 dark:text-gray-200">
              <div class="mb-3 flex items-center justify-between gap-3">
                <div>
                  <div class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="about.section.diagnostics">一键诊断</div>
                  <div id="aboutDiagHint" class="mt-1 text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
                  <button id="btnRunDiagnostics" class="rounded-xl bg-gray-900 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-black/90 disabled:opacity-60 dark:bg-white dark:text-gray-900 dark:hover:bg-gray-100" data-i18n="about.diag.generate">生成报告</button>
                  <button id="btnCopyDiagnostics" class="rounded-xl bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 transition hover:bg-gray-50 disabled:opacity-60 dark:bg-gray-950/40 dark:text-gray-200 dark:hover:bg-gray-900" data-i18n="about.diag.copy">复制</button>
                </div>
              </div>
              <textarea id="aboutDiagText" class="w-full min-h-40 resize-y rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-white/70 p-3 font-mono text-xs text-gray-700 outline-none dark:border-gray-800 dark:bg-gray-950/40 dark:text-gray-200" readonly></textarea>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-center justify-end gap-3 border-t border-gray-200 bg-white/90 px-6 py-4 backdrop-blur dark:border-gray-800 dark:bg-gray-950/90">
          <button id="btnCloseAboutBottom" class="rounded-2xl bg-white px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 transition hover:bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 dark:text-gray-300 dark:hover:bg-gray-700" data-i18n="common.close">关闭</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div id="proxyModal" class="fixed inset-0 z-50 hidden">
      <div id="proxyBackdrop" class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/50 backdrop-blur-sm opacity-0 transition-opacity"></div>
      <div id="proxyContent" class="absolute inset-x-4 top-24 bottom-8 mx-auto max-w-xl translate-y-6 overflow-hidden rounded-3xl bg-gray-50 shadow-2xl transition-transform dark:bg-gray-950">
        <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4 border-b border-gray-200 px-6 py-4 dark:border-gray-800">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white" data-i18n="proxy.title">代理设置</h2>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="proxy.subtitle">配置网络代理与 GitHub Proxy 行为</p>
          </div>
          <button id="btnCloseProxy" class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 transition hover:bg-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-800 dark:text-gray-400 dark:hover:bg-gray-700" aria-label="关闭" data-i18n-aria-label="common.close" data-i18n-title="common.close">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" />
            </svg>
          </button>
        </div>

        <div class="h-full overflow-y-auto p-6 pb-28">
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-gray-100/60 p-4 dark:bg-gray-900/40">
              <div class="grid gap-3 md:grid-cols-2">
                <div class="md:col-span-2">
                  <label class="mb-1.5 block text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="config.proxy.mode">代理模式</label>
                  <select id="cfgProxyMode" class="w-full rounded-xl bg-white px-4 py-3 text-base text-gray-900 outline-none dark:bg-gray-800 dark:text-white">
                    <option value="custom" data-i18n="config.proxy.mode.custom">自定义代理</option>
                    <option value="system" data-i18n="config.proxy.mode.system">系统代理</option>
                    <option value="smart" data-i18n="config.proxy.mode.smart">智能代理</option>
                  </select>
                </div>

                <div id="cfgHttpProxySection" class="md:col-span-2 grid gap-3 md:grid-cols-2">
                  <div class="md:col-span-2">
                    <label class="mb-1.5 block text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="config.proxy.url">代理地址</label>
                    <input id="cfgProxyUrl" type="text" class="w-full rounded-xl bg-white px-4 py-3 text-base text-gray-900 outline-none dark:bg-gray-800 dark:text-white" placeholder="http://127.0.0.1:7890" />
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <label class="mb-1.5 block text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="config.proxy.user">用户名</label>
                    <input id="cfgProxyUser" type="text" class="w-full rounded-xl bg-white px-4 py-3 text-base text-gray-900 outline-none dark:bg-gray-800 dark:text-white" placeholder="" />
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <label class="mb-1.5 block text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="config.proxy.pass">密码</label>
                    <input id="cfgProxyPass" type="password" class="w-full rounded-xl bg-white px-4 py-3 text-base text-gray-900 outline-none dark:bg-gray-800 dark:text-white" placeholder="" />
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div id="cfgGhProxySection" class="md:col-span-2">
                  <label class="mb-1.5 block text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="config.github_proxy">GitHub Proxy (ghproxy)</label>
                  <input id="cfgGhProxy" type="text" class="w-full rounded-xl bg-white px-4 py-3 text-base text-gray-900 outline-none dark:bg-gray-800 dark:text-white" placeholder="https://ghproxy.net/" />
                  <div id="cfgGhProxyQuickPick" class="mt-2"></div>
                  <p class="mt-2 text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="config.github_proxy.smart_hint">
                    仅用于 GitHub Raw 下载/远程载入；GitHub API 不使用。
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="mt-4 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-white/70 p-3 text-xs text-gray-600 dark:border-gray-800 dark:bg-gray-950/30 dark:text-gray-300" data-i18n="config.proxy.diff">
                说明：custom/system/smart 三种模式会决定是否使用自定义代理、系统代理和 github-proxy(ghproxy)。smart 模式下规则下载/远程载入优先走 ghproxy 直连；GitHub API 查询新版优先使用自定义代理。
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white/70 p-4 text-xs text-gray-600 dark:bg-gray-950/30 dark:text-gray-300" data-i18n="proxy.note">
              提示：这里的修改会即时写入当前 YAML 草稿；点击“保存配置”后才会写入到配置文件。
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="absolute right-0 bottom-0 left-0 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-end gap-2 border-t border-gray-200 bg-white/90 px-6 py-4 backdrop-blur dark:border-gray-800 dark:bg-gray-950/90">
          <button id="btnCloseProxyBottom" class="rounded-2xl bg-white px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 transition hover:bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 dark:text-gray-300 dark:hover:bg-gray-700" data-i18n="common.close">关闭</button>
          <button id="btnSaveProxy" class="rounded-2xl bg-primary-600 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-lg shadow-primary-600/25 transition-all active:scale-95 hover:bg-primary-700" data-i18n="config.save">保存配置</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div id="toast" class="pointer-events-none fixed bottom-24 left-1/2 z-50 -translate-x-1/2 translate-y-4 opacity-0 transition-all duration-300">
      <div class="rounded-full bg-gray-900 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-white shadow-xl dark:bg-white dark:text-gray-900">
        <span id="toastText" data-i18n="app.toast_default">操作成功</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <script src="../scripts/app.ts"></script>
  </body>
</html>
